1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,879
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,880 --> 00:00:32,339
=Episode 3=
(Memories of my mother)

3
00:00:32,340 --> 00:00:33,479
(is my greatest weapon)

4
00:00:33,480 --> 00:00:36,170
(against this rotten world.)

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:44,180
(He was actually wounded by me?)

6
00:00:46,900 --> 00:00:49,860
(Why do I suffer heavenly backlash
for using immortal art on a demon?)

7
00:00:51,460 --> 00:00:53,139
It's snowing.

8
00:00:53,140 --> 00:00:55,220
Come buy an umbrella.

9
00:00:57,580 --> 00:00:58,740
Miss,

10
00:00:58,900 --> 00:01:00,419
come buy an umbrella.

11
00:01:00,420 --> 00:01:01,780
The snow doesn't bother me.

12
00:01:03,980 --> 00:01:05,019
Miss,

13
00:01:05,020 --> 00:01:06,419
just take a look.

14
00:01:06,420 --> 00:01:07,739
It'd make a nice accessory.

15
00:01:07,740 --> 00:01:09,579
This color suits you well.

16
00:01:09,580 --> 00:01:10,740
Please show some respect.

17
00:01:10,860 --> 00:01:12,179
If you persist,

18
00:01:12,180 --> 00:01:13,580
don't blame me for being rude.

19
00:01:24,300 --> 00:01:25,660
I'll take the umbrella.

20
00:01:25,820 --> 00:01:26,980
Now I'm giving it to you.

21
00:01:28,140 --> 00:01:29,340
The snow's heavy.

22
00:01:29,900 --> 00:01:31,180
Head home early.

23
00:01:37,460 --> 00:01:39,460
Oh no! Master is in danger!

24
00:01:53,260 --> 00:01:55,259
How dare she injure me?

25
00:01:55,260 --> 00:01:57,780
This sword spirit must die.

26
00:02:00,180 --> 00:02:01,699
(Could that heavenly lightning just now)

27
00:02:01,700 --> 00:02:03,300
(have broken his immortal body?)

28
00:02:05,900 --> 00:02:07,780
I nearly died by your hand last night.

29
00:02:08,460 --> 00:02:10,660
Now that you've taken this stab from me,

30
00:02:10,980 --> 00:02:12,180
we're even.

31
00:02:12,460 --> 00:02:13,780
Let's part ways for good.

32
00:02:19,540 --> 00:02:20,980
Even?

33
00:02:22,980 --> 00:02:25,219
Can a hundred years of hatred

34
00:02:25,220 --> 00:02:26,980
be settled so easily?

35
00:02:40,660 --> 00:02:42,100
Heavenly Dao!

36
00:02:58,060 --> 00:03:00,340
(Empress Helian Ning of Ning)

37
00:03:02,540 --> 00:03:03,700
Mother...

38
00:03:03,740 --> 00:03:04,900
Xihe,

39
00:03:05,220 --> 00:03:07,220
this is the perfect chance.

40
00:03:13,340 --> 00:03:15,100
Kill him.

41
00:03:23,540 --> 00:03:25,860
He may be detestable,

42
00:03:26,900 --> 00:03:29,100
but he didn't take my life.

43
00:03:30,140 --> 00:03:31,740
I have no reason to kill him.

44
00:03:37,900 --> 00:03:39,300
He's a god.

45
00:03:43,900 --> 00:03:47,100
You've seen his power just now.

46
00:03:47,660 --> 00:03:50,420
If he recovers, you won't escape.

47
00:03:53,420 --> 00:03:54,780
Now,

48
00:03:55,220 --> 00:03:57,300
stab here.

49
00:03:57,340 --> 00:03:59,220
Destroy his divine heart,

50
00:03:59,420 --> 00:04:01,180
and end this forever.

51
00:04:15,140 --> 00:04:17,420
Have you forgotten what he did to you?

52
00:04:17,580 --> 00:04:19,100
He injured your body,

53
00:04:19,580 --> 00:04:21,219
defiled your dignity,

54
00:04:21,220 --> 00:04:22,780
and took your heart.

55
00:04:23,540 --> 00:04:25,460
Even a thousand stabs

56
00:04:26,540 --> 00:04:28,460
would not be excessive for him.

57
00:04:31,460 --> 00:04:32,980
I've protected you for years.

58
00:04:33,140 --> 00:04:34,620
Why won't you listen?

59
00:04:35,780 --> 00:04:37,299
You useless thing!

60
00:04:37,300 --> 00:04:38,460
Do it now!

61
00:04:42,980 --> 00:04:44,140
Come on.

62
00:04:46,460 --> 00:04:47,780
Do it.

63
00:04:51,780 --> 00:04:53,219
Kill your own husband

64
00:04:53,220 --> 00:04:54,420
once again.

65
00:04:57,140 --> 00:04:58,860
Do it!

66
00:05:10,420 --> 00:05:11,580
As expected...

67
00:05:12,220 --> 00:05:14,220
you're still you.

68
00:05:16,770 --> 00:05:21,600
♪When starlight cuts
through the long night♪

69
00:05:23,930 --> 00:05:29,300
♪It bids farewell to another blue sky♪

70
00:05:29,780 --> 00:05:30,940
Kill him!

71
00:05:31,060 --> 00:05:32,159
What are you waiting for?

72
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:33,949
♪To see is to part again♪

73
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:36,099
♪To stay is to wish for forever♪

74
00:05:36,100 --> 00:05:37,859
Won't you even listen
to your mother now?

75
00:05:37,860 --> 00:05:42,139
♪Counting every moment,
unwilling to pause♪

76
00:05:42,140 --> 00:05:43,420
Xihe,

77
00:05:43,860 --> 00:05:46,220
you don't have to listen
to me in everything.

78
00:05:46,460 --> 00:05:47,780
What you should listen to

79
00:05:47,900 --> 00:05:49,540
is your own heart.

80
00:05:52,460 --> 00:05:53,620
Stab him.

81
00:05:53,980 --> 00:05:55,220
Kill him!

82
00:06:02,100 --> 00:06:03,779
How dare you stab your own mother?

83
00:06:03,780 --> 00:06:04,940
Enough.

84
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:07,620
You're not my mother.

85
00:06:08,580 --> 00:06:10,980
My mother always told me
to follow my own heart,

86
00:06:11,300 --> 00:06:13,540
not to obey her blindly.

87
00:06:13,900 --> 00:06:16,220
She is the best mother in the world.

88
00:06:16,540 --> 00:06:18,660
I won't allow anyone to defile her.

89
00:06:22,220 --> 00:06:24,020
(Little Immortal,)

90
00:06:24,460 --> 00:06:26,300
(you're lucky.)

91
00:06:29,340 --> 00:06:31,180
I hurt you again just now.

92
00:06:31,940 --> 00:06:33,180
I don't like owing debts.

93
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:36,060
Let me get you inside before I go.

94
00:06:36,740 --> 00:06:37,900
Call it saving you.

95
00:06:38,700 --> 00:06:40,180
Then we're even.

96
00:06:40,580 --> 00:06:41,740
And you,

97
00:06:42,100 --> 00:06:43,780
stop pestering me.

98
00:06:45,980 --> 00:06:47,700
I don't need your help.

99
00:06:52,220 --> 00:06:53,540
You're beyond saving.

100
00:07:08,860 --> 00:07:10,900
They're the ones
who were after me in the city.

101
00:07:11,100 --> 00:07:12,420
Flower Slaves.

102
00:07:12,460 --> 00:07:13,820
Aren't you leaving?

103
00:07:14,340 --> 00:07:15,540
Then go.

104
00:07:15,700 --> 00:07:18,300
I suggest you
drop that brooding look of yours.

105
00:07:18,340 --> 00:07:19,099
Otherwise,

106
00:07:19,100 --> 00:07:20,260
we'll both die.

107
00:07:20,860 --> 00:07:22,339
Since you recognize them,

108
00:07:22,340 --> 00:07:24,060
is there a way to deal with them?

109
00:07:24,180 --> 00:07:25,820
(A seer?)

110
00:07:25,940 --> 00:07:27,339
(I see now.)

111
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:29,499
(When a god uses techniques on humans,)

112
00:07:29,500 --> 00:07:31,859
(he suffers heavenly backlash)

113
00:07:31,860 --> 00:07:33,859
(and loses his power.)

114
00:07:33,860 --> 00:07:34,819
(Last time,)

115
00:07:34,820 --> 00:07:36,379
(she was taken by Ye Zhao.)

116
00:07:36,380 --> 00:07:37,219
(This time,)

117
00:07:37,220 --> 00:07:39,499
(I will take her back.)

118
00:07:39,500 --> 00:07:41,020
Clan members,

119
00:07:41,220 --> 00:07:44,060
this is
a once-in-a-thousand-years chance.

120
00:07:44,860 --> 00:07:48,180
(Flower Slave Clan Leader, Zhang Muzhi)
This is our chance to slay a god and seize her!

121
00:07:48,460 --> 00:07:50,380
To Baihua Hall now!

122
00:07:55,860 --> 00:07:59,660
The agony of the past hundred years

123
00:08:00,460 --> 00:08:02,660
ends today.

124
00:08:02,860 --> 00:08:06,180
Curse you, heavens!
You've been real good to me!

125
00:08:33,470 --> 00:08:35,179
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

126
00:08:35,180 --> 00:08:38,029
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

127
00:08:38,030 --> 00:08:40,769
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

128
00:08:40,770 --> 00:08:42,399
♪Let the long shadows♪

129
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:48,000
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

130
00:08:48,050 --> 00:08:49,649
♪If in a dream♪

131
00:08:49,650 --> 00:08:52,409
♪I can hear your voice♪

132
00:08:52,410 --> 00:08:55,259
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

133
00:08:55,260 --> 00:08:57,859
♪Let it be us♪

134
00:08:57,860 --> 00:09:02,649
♪drawing endlessly close♪

135
00:09:02,650 --> 00:09:04,409
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

136
00:09:04,410 --> 00:09:07,060
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

137
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:09,999
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

138
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,649
♪Not even in time♪

139
00:09:11,650 --> 00:09:17,309
♪to tell you how I feel♪

140
00:09:17,310 --> 00:09:18,849
♪If the rain won't stop♪

141
00:09:18,850 --> 00:09:21,599
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

142
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:24,569
♪Let love go on♪

143
00:09:24,570 --> 00:09:27,119
♪Until forever♪

144
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:31,759
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

145
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:34,369
♪Until forever♪

146
00:09:34,370 --> 00:09:41,480
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
